      • canCauseContainmentProblems

        public final boolean canCauseContainmentProblems()
        Determine whether or not this token is capable of causing a containment problem. If a token can cause canContain to return false when it's passed in as containedType, then it must return true. This is used to improve the performance of ASTokenFixer.locateBottommostContainerProblem.
        Returns:
        true iff the token can cause canContain to return false.
